Overview

This HTML document represents a billing/receipt page for a Smart Supermarket web application. It displays customer purchase details, itemized billing, tax calculation, and provides options to print the bill or start a new transaction.

üß± Structure Description
1. Document Setup
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">


Declares the document as HTML5.

Sets the language to English.

2. Head Section
<head>


Contains metadata and external resources:

Character Encoding

<meta charset="UTF-8">


Ensures proper text rendering.

Responsive Design

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">


Makes the page mobile-friendly.

Title

<title>Bill - Smart Supermarket</title>


Displayed in the browser tab.

External CSS

<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">


Links the stylesheet for layout and design.

3. Body Section
<body>


Contains all visible content.

üßæ Bill Layout
4. Main Container
<div class="bill-container">


Wraps the entire bill for styling and alignment.

5. Bill Header
<div class="bill-header">


Displays store and bill information:

Store name: SMART SUPERMARKET

Thank-you message

Bill details dynamically filled using JavaScript:

Bill number

Date

Time

Machine number

Each detail uses <span> elements with IDs for dynamic updates.

6. Itemized Bill Table
<table class="bill-table">


Displays purchased items:

Column	Description
Item	Product name
Qty	Quantity purchased
Price	Price per unit
Total	Price √ó Quantity
<tbody id="billItems">


Items are loaded dynamically via JavaScript.

7. Bill Summary Section
<div class="bill-summary">


Shows payment calculations:

Subtotal

Tax (5%)

Grand Total

Each value is dynamically updated using JavaScript.

8. Footer Section
<div class="bill-footer">


Contains:

Thank-you message

Print Bill button

onclick="window.print()"


Opens the print dialog.

New Transaction button

onclick="window.location.href='index.html'"


Redirects to the home page.

9. JavaScript Integration
<script src="js/bill.js"></script>


Handles:

Loading bill data

Calculating totals and tax

Updating dynamic content

‚úÖ Key Features

Dynamic bill generation

Responsive design

Printable receipt

Easy navigation for new transactions

Clean and structured layout

